  METHOD test001_14.

* first two lines should fail
    _code 'ASSIGN COMPONENT lv_string OF STRUCTURE ls_foo TO <lg_data>.'.
    _code 'ASSIGN COMPONENT lv_string OF STRUCTURE ls_foo TO <lg_data>.'.
